        "TileImage": "$($repository 2fa9698f-eb9b-4991-8aaf-3bddcf23e247).Image",
        "Description": "As evening settled over the reef, SquidwardBobi brewed a warm cup of sea tea and sat by his window. The water glowed softly, but the quiet felt a little heavier than before.\r\rHe played one last gentle tune on his clarinet, slower this time, each note lingering. When it ended, the silence returned, deeper than he expected.\r\rSquidwardBobi sighed softly. Life was peaceful, just as he wanted—but sometimes, in that calm, he couldn’t help feeling a little alone.",
